WEBVTT

00:07:58.441 --> 00:08:01.258
kiuhalisia inaelezea mchoro

00:08:01.282 --> 00:08:04.797
zaidi ya ungesema, "Sasa, kuna treni
inayotokea sehemu palipo na moto,

00:08:04.821 --> 00:08:06.907
na kuna vinara katika pazia

00:08:06.931 --> 00:08:09.594
Itaonekana kisicho cha kawaida
kusema kisichokuwepo,

00:08:09.618 --> 00:08:11.655
lakini ni nyenzo yenye thamani.

00:08:12.398 --> 00:08:15.158
Pale mpelezi aliyejifunza kuhusu
uono wa maarifa

00:08:15.182 --> 00:08:16.333
huko Carolina Kaskazini

00:08:16.357 --> 00:08:17.833
aliitwa katika eneo la tukio,

00:08:17.857 --> 00:08:19.297
ilikuwa mashua yenye majeruhi,

00:08:19.321 --> 00:08:22.881
na shuhuda alimwambia huyu mpelelezi
kwamba mashua ilipinduka

00:08:22.905 --> 00:08:25.616
na aliyekuwepo alizama chini.

00:08:26.055 --> 00:08:29.705
Sasa, kwa haraka, wapelelezi wa uhalifu
huangalia kile kinachoonekana,

00:08:29.729 --> 00:08:31.929
lakini mpelelezi huyu
alifanya kitu tofauti.